summary: This code file contains the interface for the TCRefrection class, which is part of the AIThinkingControl module. It has two methods: refrection that takes an AICansetModel and a DemandModel as parameters, and actionRefrection that takes a TOFoModel as a parameter. Both methods return a boolean value.
